snippet.title: Hitman: World of Assassination - The Drop Trailer | Xbox @ Gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
Check out the trailer for Hitman: World of Assassination - The Drop, the new DLC where Agent 47 hunts down a world-famous EDM DJ (voiced by superstar DJ Dimitri Vegas). The Drop releases October 2023.
